snippet.textDisplay:
Rohail really knows how to make arrangements to make both the singers and the instrumentalists shine.

There is room for them all to breathe, which is what the other producers couldn't master in his absence. The piece isn't congested, it flows and is really easy on the ears - which is how music should be ❤
